    <text type="letter">
        <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.02554.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when="1876-12-20"><choice>
                            <abbr>Dec</abbr>
                            <expan>December</expan>
                        </choice> 20 '76</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>My dear Johnston</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Enclosed find check for &#36;35 for which send me on <hi rend="underline">immediately</hi> 
                as good a <hi rend="underline">gold watch</hi>, hunting case,
                middling showy in appearance &#38; best inside you can give me for that sum. (Let me
                have it at wholesale price, only paying yourself what you pay for it). I want it for
                a Christmas present for a young man<ptr target="loc.02554_n1"/>&#8212;
                <hi rend="underline">Can't you send it by express to-night or tomorrow morning
                early?</hi></p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
                <address>
                    <addrLine>431 Stevens st cor West</addrLine>
                    <addrLine>Camden New Jersey</addrLine>
                </address>
            </closer> 
            <postscript>
                <p>I might as well leave you some margin. If you think of something a little more
                    price or different any how, better, send it along, as it can be changed, paid
                    for, or made right when I come on in January&#8212;</p>
                <p>I<ptr target="loc.02554_n2"/> find I have no revenue stamp to put on check &#38; cannot go out to get
                    one&#8212;</p>
            </postscript>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.02554.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
    </text> 
